this class is too simple to represent the TOSCA.  
it should at least include below:
    Metadata serviceMetadata;
    private Service catalogService;
    ISdcCsarHelper sdcCsarHelper; this may be put into decoder part.
    List<NodeTemplate> allottedList;
    List<NodeTemplate> networkTypes;
    List<NodeTemplate> vfTypes;

and use ToscaResource as a wrapper, and btw, the Tosca file name/path should be a standard format: policy side setting as prefix+ Iartifact from sdc . Don't need a class to record each file
